  <summary date="2007-10-04T19:52:43Z" status="Introduced in House">Trade Advisory Committee Reform Act or the TAC Act - Amends the Trade Act of 1974 to: (1) revise the selection process for congressional advisers for trade policy and negotiations; and (2) expand the duties of such congressional advisers, including to provide recommendations to executive officials on trade agreement effects and to provide for the appointment of members to a trade advisory committee.

Establishes a Public Health Advisory Committee on Trade.</summary>
